    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017980/extras/87189a6ccaab01715d4e1c4ddbfd3347.avif?t=1762183933\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017980/extras_big/87189a6ccaab01715d4e1c4ddbfd3347.webp?t=1762183933 width=1560 height=1084 /></span>A family 3D collectathon platformer video game featuring 200 addictive levels.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A digital virus has corrupted DigiWorld, and the bots within are now under the control of the evil MegaBot. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world’s fate lies on the small shoulders of a defective bot untouched by the virus named Digi.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >He must collect all the DigiOrbs released by DigiWorld’s antivirus defence system. Digi may be too small to face the corrupted bots head-on, but he can dodge his way to saving the DigiWorld.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Digi get Dodging!!!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017980/extras/e874d2654cd44810159bef675de6f3f3.avif?t=1762183933\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017980/extras_big/e874d2654cd44810159bef675de6f3f3.webp?t=1762183933 width=1560 height=812 /></span></p>",
